Epigenetic Effects of Healthy Foods and Lifestyle Habits from the Southern 
European Atlantic Diet Pattern: A Narrative Review.

Lorenzo PM(1)(2), Izquierdo AG(1)(2), Rodriguez-Carnero G(1)(3), Fernández-Pombo 
