Pharmaceutical and nutraceutical activation of FOXO3 for healthy longevity.

McIntyre RL(1), Liu YJ(1), Hu M(1), Morris BJ(2), Willcox BJ(3), Donlon TA(4), 
Houtkooper RH(1), Janssens GE(5).

Author information:
(1)Laboratory Genetic Metabolic Diseases, Amsterdam Gastroenterology, 
Endocrinology, and Metabolism, Amsterdam Cardiovascular Sciences, Amsterdam 
University Medical Centers, University of Amsterdam, Amsterdam, The Netherlands.
(2)School of Medical Sciences, University of Sydney, Sydney, NSW, Australia; 
Department of Research, Kuakini Medical Center, Honolulu, HI, USA; Department of 
Geriatric Medicine, John A. Burns School of Medicine, University of Hawaii, 
Honolulu, HI, USA.
(3)Department of Research, Kuakini Medical Center, Honolulu, HI, USA; Department 
of Geriatric Medicine, John A. Burns School of Medicine, University of Hawaii, 
